data.description: Adorable ranch home in the Waverly School district. Home features a large eat- in kitchen, sunken living room and a basement with a waterproofing system. There is a garage for extra storage and a fenced in backyard. Seller has made many updates including new roof (2021) and new water heater (2021), move right in and enjoy.
